fg_segments: 1. PRIVACY AND COOKIE STATEMENT (Version 1.8 dated August 2017)
The Privacy Statement helps you understand how ODEON may collect and use your personal information, and the choices you can make about how your personal information is used.
2. LIMITLESS TERMS AND CONDITIONS (Version 2.31 dated September 2017)
The Limitless terms and conditions set out the legally binding terms which apply to everyone who joins Limitless.
3. ODEON PREMIÈRE CLUB CARD TERMS AND CONDITIONS (Version 5.1 dated September 2017)

The ODEON Première Club Terms and Conditions set out the legally binding terms which apply to everyone who joins the Republic of Ireland ODEON Première Club, and/or uses a Republic of Ireland ODEON Première Club Card.
Version 4.0 contains changes to points expiry windows (see paragraphs 22 and 23).
" 4. TICKET PURCHASE TERMS AND CONDITIONS (Version 3.4 dated September 2017)
The Ticket Purchase Terms and Conditions set out the legally binding terms which apply to the purchase of a ticket online at odeoncinemas.ie.
5. WEBSITE TERMS OF USE (Version 1.3 dated August 2017)
The Website Terms of Use set out the legally binding terms which apply to everyone who accesses or uses our website at odeoncinemas.ie.
6. GENERAL ADMISSION TERMS (Version 1.0 dated March 2012)
The General Admission Terms set out the legally binding terms generally applicable to the issue of a ticket and to your subsequent access to an ODEON Cinema in the Republic of Ireland.
7. ODEON GIFT CARD TERMS AND CONDITIONS (Version 2.3 dated September 2017)
TThe ODEON GIFT CARD Terms and Conditions set out the legally binding terms which apply to everyone who purchases a Republic of Ireland ODEON Gift Card.
It also contains the legally binding Terms and Conditions of Use for a Republic of Ireland ODEON GIFT CARD.8.
ODEON SOCIAL MEDIA PRIZE DRAW TERMS AND CONDITIONS (Version 1.1 dated April 2016)
These terms set out the legally binding terms and conditions which apply to the series of prize draws we run on our social media channels unless otherwise stated.
This includes http://www.Facebook.com/ODEONCinemasIreland.9. LIMITLESS GIFT MEMBERSHIP CARD & VOUCHER CODE

TERMS OF USE (Version 1.0 dated September 2017) The Limitless Gift Membership Card & Voucher Code Terms of Use set out the legally binding terms which apply to everyone who uses a Limitless gift membership card or voucher code.
10. ODEON WI-FI TERMS OF USE (Version 1.2 dated August 2017)
The Wi-Fi Terms of Use set out the legally binding terms and conditions which apply to the use of ODEON wi-fi in cinemas.
11. MYODEON ONLINE DISCOUNT TERMS AND CONDITIONS (Version 1.0 dated September 2017)
The MYODEON Online Discount Terms and Conditions set out the legally binding terms and conditions which apply to the MYODEON Online Discount offer.
COMPANY INFORMATION UNITED CINEMAS INTERNATIONAL (IRELAND) LIMITED Company number 441782.
Vat No: IE9694881P For more information about how to contact us, please visit the Contact Us page of this website.
